title: 🐝 "When you're accustomed to privilege, equality feels like oppression." - Mike Jebbett
content: Build a fixed list combobox. A fixed list combo box is when a user can type a certain string, and there is a list of strings that is designed to help the user arrive at a value. Here is an example of one! Build something that will take in a set of strings and return matching suggestions as the user types.
